  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were thousands of people, all Jewish with children, with-- old and young, and everybody was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden we see, during the day, it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of a sudden I see the militia, the Jewish police from the Jewish community center, from the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He-- they divided, they made like a chain to separate the people from that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I-- and all of a sudden we see a young-- young man, police also, the Jewish police, police-- militia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he approached us, and he said-- no, then Mom, my [INAUDIBLE], pardon me, Mom she realizes something is going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So she put down a white, she-- so could see that the people what had the white belt, they were going to the other direction.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So she just-- she was a very beautiful lady, and she was strong, so she took the-- she had a lot of courage, she put the white belt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She noticed one of militia was a husband of our dentist, so I think she was a little more secure.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she just tore through the-- the chain, and she went to through there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they tried to stop her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She said, my husband is there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they let her through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then she waved to us that we should come, both of us, I and my sister, so which we did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And coming there, the policeman who show to the-- he was a German, sitting German, SS, whoever they are, by the table.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he took us, the young man, which I later found out was a friend of mine, coincidentally went together to school, to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So his name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Siglund ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He just took us around like this, and he said, this is the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
